<BaseLayout title="Development Reports — Property Potential Analysis" description="Zoning compliance and property development potential reports. Know what you can build before you buy. Town planners Cape Town.">
<section class="min-h-[50vh] flex items-center"><div class="wrap pt-28 pb-16"><span class="tag mb-10">Services · Reports</span><h1 class="mb-6">Development <span class="text-accent">reports</span></h1><p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg">Know what your property can become — before you buy, develop, or invest. Delivered in 5–7 working days.</p></div></section>
<div class="wrap pb-24"><div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-border-subtle">
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Zoning compliance</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Verify lawful use of a property. Essential for business licences, property transfers, and liquor licence applications.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Development potential</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Full assessment: maximum density, building envelope, permitted uses, and potential for rezoning or subdivision.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Building envelope</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Coverage, FAR, height, and building line analysis. Know exactly what footprint you can build.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Municipal policy</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Spatial development frameworks, structure plans and precinct plans — the rules that shape development.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Buyers & investors</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Don't buy a property without knowing its full potential. Our reports find value others miss.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Real estate agents</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Add a development potential report to your listing. Helps sell properties with extra development upside.</p></div>
</div></div>
<section class="py-32 text-center border-t border-border-subtle"><div class="narrow"><h2 class="mb-6">Know before you <span class="text-accent">buy</span></h2><p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-10">Get a property development potential report in 5–7 days.</p><a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-base px-8 py-4">Get Your Free Consultation</a></div></section>
</BaseLayout>